The paper also discusses the dynamics of SNN and their ability to implement algorithms, which is related to control systems and robotics. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the theoretical understanding of SNN algorithms, which is related to artificial intelligence.
